            "description": "At the Consumer Electronic Show (CES) in Las Vegas, Google showed Android 3.0, Honeycomb.\nIt is the next version of the Android platform, designed for devices with larger screen sizes, such as tablets.\u00a0 Honeycomb is said to provide a &#8220;truly virtual and holographic user interface.&#8221;\n\n\u00a0",
            "content:encoded": "<p>At the Consumer Electronic Show (CES) in Las Vegas, Google showed <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/googlemobile.blogspot.com\/2011\/01\/sneak-peak-of-android-30-honeycomb.html\">Android 3.0<\/a>, Honeycomb.<\/p>\n<p>It is the next version of the Android platform, designed for devices with larger screen sizes, such as tablets.\u00a0 Honeycomb is said to provide a &#8220;truly virtual and holographic user interface.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p><\/p> \n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=FF59wp6KWV8:XX6qx6s6sL0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=FF59wp6KWV8:XX6qx6s6sL0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=FF59wp6KWV8:XX6qx6s6sL0:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?i=FF59wp6KWV8:XX6qx6s6sL0:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"><\/a>\n<\/div>",
