            "guid": {
                "isPermaLink": "false",
                "content": "http:\/\/ajaxian.com\/?p=10505"
            },
            "description": "Per James Newton, the latest Json.NET release targets .NET 4. Json.NET 4.0 comes with a Windows Phone specific dll, compiled using Windows Phone tools. A .NET 4 feature employed is the dynamic keyword, which allows variables and members to be statically typed as dynamic.\u00a0 Json.NET 4.0 adds support for dynamic keywords in a couple of [...]",
            "content:encoded": "<p>Per <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/james.newtonking.com\">James Newton<\/a>, the latest Json.NET release targets .NET 4. <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/james.newtonking.com\/archive\/2011\/01\/03\/json-net-4-0-release-1-net-4-and-windows-phone-support.aspx\">Json.NET 4.0<\/a> comes with a Windows Phone specific dll, compiled using Windows Phone tools. A .NET 4 feature employed is the dynamic keyword, which allows variables and members to be statically typed as dynamic.\u00a0 Json.NET 4.0 adds support for dynamic keywords in a couple of areas.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>The first and less visible of the two is in the JsonSerializer. Because there is no static list of fields or properties for a dynamic type the serializer interrogates the value for its members prior to serializing and deserializing. The end result is serializing should Just Work for any type that implements IDynamicMetaObjectProvider.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=4bN1wi-rK2U:NRLzgnyj3ds:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=4bN1wi-rK2U:NRLzgnyj3ds:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=4bN1wi-rK2U:NRLzgnyj3ds:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?i=4bN1wi-rK2U:NRLzgnyj3ds:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"><\/a>\n<\/div>",
