            "description": "Cross document messaging is addressed in a recent HTML5 Web Messaging Working draft from the redoubtable W3C. The proposed messaging system is said to &#8220;allow documents to communicate with each other regardless of their source domain, in a way designed to not enable cross-site scripting attacks.&#8221; For more on the w3C draft, go to its [...]",
            "content:encoded": "<p>Cross document messaging is addressed in a recent HTML5 Web Messaging Working draft from the redoubtable W3C. The proposed messaging system is said to &#8220;allow documents to communicate with each other regardless of their source domain, in a way designed to not enable cross-site scripting attacks.&#8221; For more on the w3C draft, go to its <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/TR\/2010\/WD-webmessaging-20101118\/\">HTML5 Web Messaging page<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=lYpsK_S-W2A:smOnIeqM3T4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=lYpsK_S-W2A:smOnIeqM3T4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=lYpsK_S-W2A:smOnIeqM3T4:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?i=lYpsK_S-W2A:smOnIeqM3T4:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"><\/a>\n<\/div>",
