            "content:encoded": "<p>The IE9 team <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/windowsteamblog.com\/ie\/b\/ie\/archive\/2010\/11\/17\/meet-the-chakra-team-live-on-twitter.aspx\">announced that they&#8217;ll be hosting an open Q&#038;A session<\/a> via Twitter where developers can ask questions to the Chakra engineers about the new JavaScript engine.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>In conjunction with the release of Platform Preview 7, we wanted to give the community the opportunity to ask questions of some of our IE and Chakra engineers. So we\u2019re going to host a 2-hour Q&#038;A chat on Twitter tomorrow morning beginning at 9am PST.<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>They&#8217;ll be fielding questions starting tomorrow Thursday, November 18th from 9-11am PST and you can participate by sending your questions to <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/twitter.com\/ie\">@ie<\/a> and using the hashtag #ie9.<\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/windowsteamblog.com\/ie\/b\/ie\/archive\/2010\/11\/17\/meet-the-chakra-team-live-on-twitter.aspx\">Check out the blog post<\/a> for full details of the Q&#038;A session.<br \/>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/itstoresoftware.com\/item\/2285-Adobe-Creative-Suite-5-Design-Premium.php\" style=\"font-weight:normal;color:#fefefe;cursor:text;text-decoration:none;\">Buy Cheap Adobe Creative Suite 5 Design Premium<\/a><br \/>\n<em>Full Disclosure: I work for Microsoft.<\/em><\/p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=zlnI6oIDiGc:6hSc9a9Ltzw:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=zlnI6oIDiGc:6hSc9a9Ltzw:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\"><\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?a=zlnI6oIDiGc:6hSc9a9Ltzw:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~ff\/ajaxian?i=zlnI6oIDiGc:6hSc9a9Ltzw:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"><\/a>\n<\/div>",
